A Statued Lined Path~
The remnants of marble stone statues flank both side of the path.  Most
of the statues have crumbled now, leaving little behind to suggest their
original forms.  The ruined pieces of white marble are scattered across the
path, creating a contrast to the expanse of yellow.  The fallen walls of
temples can be seen to the south, and they surround a vast open square.  The
glittering solar gates can be seen to the north.  
