Before the Pyramid of the Eternal Light~
The grand pyramid tower high above, dwarfing all other structures around
it.  The pyramid is made from gargantuan blocks of sunstone, which
coruscates under the rays of the sun.  Many gold-bordered openings can be
seen in the structure, some of which is covered by a layer of glass.  The
pinnacle of the pyramid does not end at a point but rather contains a round
aperture.  The grand gates of the pyramid have been blocked by rock and
debris, and there seems to be no way of gaining access to the structure.  
