House of the Setting Sun~
The House of the Setting Sun stands alone on the eastern hill, its
entrance forever facing the direction of the setting sun.  The building's
eastern wall, the one facing the eastern wind, lies buried under a blanket
of thin sand.  Four pillars surround the structure, and a single flame burns
at the pinnacle of each pillar.  The thick iron doors of the house have been
flung open, revealing the ominous darkness inside that seems to engulf all
light.  
